            "id": 5940581,
            "title": "外資近5日買超個股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 外資累計買超 5 日的股票<br/>新光金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2888:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2888-TW</a>)、群益優選非投等債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00953B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00953B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00953B-TW</a>)、如興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4414:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4414\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4414-TW</a>)、復華台灣科技優息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00929:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00929\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00929-TW</a>)、統一台灣高息動能 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00939:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00939\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00939-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 外資累計買超 4 日的股票<br/>新光金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2888:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2888-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_sel